Name: Value
Description: Identifies the value to which the cell(s) defined in GridAttachment should be fixed. Supports the use of meaningful leading or trailing spaces. Note that care should be taken to make sure this is a valid value within the response domain of the cell.

Name: GridAttachment
Description: Identifies the cell or cells in a grid to which the label is attached by a reference to a specific cell coordinate in a grid or by identifying a range of values along a dimension.
